      "message": "Initially, I was hoping that this could go away entirely, but I see that visitProxies is used by both GrPipeline and GrProcessorSet. When GrProcessorSet can go away after John\u0027s FP chaining fixes, maybe we can just move this into GrPipeline\u0027s visitProxies?",
