      "writtenOn": "2020-07-09T16:07:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That makes sense to me.\n\nFWIW I did try modifying this so that I didn\u0027t have to add visitTextureEffects. It got complicated because I had to update VisitProxyFunc to take parameters that only made sense for sampled textures. But we use VisitProxyFunc to visit things like rendering destinations and it started to feel like I was stretching it too far to my purpose.",
